batman is a fictional character created by the artist bob kane and writer bill finger a comic book superhero batman first appeared in detective comics 27 may 1939 and since then has appeared in many of dc comics publicationshe central fixed event in the batman stories is the character s origin story as a little boy bruce wayne is horrified and traumatized to see his parents the physician dr thomas wayne and his wife martha being murdered by a mugger in front of his very eyes this drives him to fight crime in gotham city as batman
